Description: Sailor Moon fights for justice in the name of the Moon and the mysterious Moon Princess. Along the way, she recruits other girls to be Sailor Scouts and join her fight against evil.
Title: SAILOR MOON, VOL. 7
Author: Naoko Takeuchi

Description: Naruto must battle an army of the undead controlled by Kabuto, who may also be controlling Itachi.
Title: NARUTO, VOL. 58
Author: Masashi Kishimoto

Description: From the publisher: "Darkness covers the earth, and the world is under the control of evil." Who will rise up to fight for good?
Title: NAOKI URASAWA'S 20TH CENTURY BOYS, VOL. 22
Author: Naoki Urasawa

Description: In this reimagining of Lewis Carroll's "Alice's Adventures in Wonderland," the Cheshire Cat, disguised as a human named Boris, vies for Alice's affections.
Title: ALICE IN THE COUNTRY OF CLOVER: CHESHIRE CAT WALTZ, VOL. 2
Author: QuinRose

Description: This series is about grade-school boys who want to become professionals in the manga industry.
Title: BAKUMAN, VOL. 14
Author: Tsugumi Ohba

Description: This series is about an incredibly positive young girl named Yotsuba. In this volume, she explores her world through her new camera.
Title: YOTSUBA&!, VOL. 11
Author: Kiyohiko Azuma

Description: Ichigo Kurosaki sees dead people and must help usher them safely into the afterlife. In this volume: Ichigo gets more training in his abilities from his father.
Title: BLEACH, VOL. 47
Author: Tite Kubo

Description: Akitsu Masanosuke is a samurai without a lord. Will he run into more trouble when he becomes the bodyguard of the leader of the mysterious "Five Leaves" gang?
Title: HOUSE OF FIVE LEAVES, VOL. 8
Author: Natsume Ono

Description: Is this the end of humanity? It sure looks that way when what is left of mankind must go into hiding to escape the giant humanoids known as the Titans.
Title: ATTACK ON TITAN, VOL. 2
Author: Hajime Isayama

Description: Are the magical dreams of Madoka Kaname suddenly becoming a reality?
Title: PUELLA MAGI MADOKA MAGICA, VOL. 2
Author: Magica Quartet Staff
